test_positive_range:
assert [8, 9] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 8
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [8, 9]
test_even_range:
assert [-16, -18] == [-18]
  At index 0 diff: -16 != -18
  Left contains one more item: -18
  Full diff:
  - [-18]
  + [-16, -18]
test_large_range:
assert [7, 8] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 7
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [7, 8]
